        borders(regions="poland", size=1, fill="#D3D3D3") +
        coord_fixed(1.6) +
        geom_point(aes(color = city, size = city_count), alpha=0.5) +
        labs(color = "miasto", size = "liczba zapyta≈Ñ") +
        scale_size_continuous(range = c(1, 30)) +

        theme_void(base_size=20)
